    "causal_summary": "Before any rename, the in-scope surface must be frozen into a bijective, fully-classified rename map partitioned by dependency closure. Every candidate must be classified exactly once (rename/exempt/frozen/generated/tool-mandated) with no 'unknown' bucket, and the map hashed with BASE so execution is reproducible.",
